metadata.name: VI7A SENS COLLECTION BY SOLIMAN LOPEZ
metadata.description: An unprecedented Digital-Bioart NFT collection designed by the artist Solimán López that supposes an historical step in the connection between live entities, the digital, its integration into the blockchain ecosystems and the NFT production.Through this artwork we are for the very first time create a dynamic NFT fed by live cells directly from the SENS Research Foundation’s Research Center in Silicon Valley, California.
